    "The previous names that characterised this industry or sale channel were e-business, e-seller, etc.",
    "The newest trend in the research into dynamic pricing in e-commerce can be represented by a separate cluster with a focus on policy, revenue, parameters, features (of models), revenue and financial performance.",
